<br>
I used the last name &quot;Remnara' because I thought it would be fun to RP a relative of one of the guild leaders...  In this case, Gygus Remnara a paladin trainer in Freeport.  Plus, I thought the name &quot;Remnara&quot; sounded good.  I almost used &quot;D'Lere&quot; but the roleplaying would have been a bit too intense for me...  Plus, who would marry someone with that last name?<br>
<br>
On an editorial note, I must say that I agree with Verant's naming policy and report violations every time I see them.  Names that are stupid or just rip offs take away the atmosphere that EQ was trying to create.  It's bad enough that no one roleplays, but dumb names (like Sephirothh or Replay) just kind of tick me off...  I know this will make me unpopular.  Oh well. <p>Valahan Remnara<BR>Knight of Truth and Paladin of 22 seasons<BR>Luclin Server<BR>
